Class CodelistClient

java.lang.Object
com.stag.identity.shared.grpc.client.CodelistClient
@Service public class CodelistClient extends Object

Codelist gRPC Client

gRPC client for codelist-service communication. Fetches localized codelist meanings for person data enrichment with circuit breaker and retry patterns for resilience. Optimizes calls by skipping requests with no meaningful data.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jakub Pavlíček
